

PREREQUISITES
=============

Required
--------

  * Perl 5.8.9+             <http://perl.org/>
  * quvi tool 0.2.16.1+     <http://quvi.sourceforge.net/>
  * Getopt::ArgvFile        <http://search.cpan.org/perldoc?Getopt::ArgvFile>
  * JSON::XS                <http://search.cpan.org/perldoc?JSON::XS>
  * curl tool               <http://curl.haxx.se/>

Additionally, to install:
-------------------------

  * ExtUtils::MakeMaker <http://search.cpan.org/perldoc?ExtUtils::MakeMaker>


INSTALLATION
============

Notes
-----

Uninstall earlier versions of clive if you have any installed.

For the impatient
-----------------

Assuming you have installed the prerequisites to your system already,
just run "bin/clive" without installing it.

Typical installation
--------------------

To install:

  perl Makefile.PL
  make
  make install

  * Note that you can specify install prefix with INSTALL_BASE
    e.g. perl Makefile.PL INSTALL_BASE=/usr/local

Recommended reading if you are new to ExtUtils::MakeMaker:
  * <http://search.cpan.org/perldoc?ExtUtils::MakeMaker>
  * <http://perldoc.perl.org/ExtUtils/MakeMaker/FAQ.html>


